# Real-VPS test config for stand-realvps-test.sh. Copy to a location the container reads
# (/etc/vpnpool/.env.real inside the stand) — NEVER commit the filled-in version (it holds
# node secrets). The stand .gitignore already excludes .env.real.
#
# REAL_LINK is the full vless:// reality+vision share link of the node to test.
REAL_LINK="vless://UUID@HOST:443?type=tcp&security=reality&pbk=PUBKEY&sid=SHORTID&sni=www.microsoft.com&fp=chrome&flow=xtls-rprx-vision&spx=%2F#my-node"
